serverSide

Class ComHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • serverSide.ComHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChefInterface, StudentInterface, WaiterInterface, java.lang.Runnable

    public class ComHandler
extends java.lang.Thread
implements StudentInterface, WaiterInterface, ChefInterface
    Definition of the service provider agent thread for this solution of the Restaurant's Problem, implementing the client-server model of type 2 (server replication) with static launching of the entities envolved. The communication is based on the exchange of object of type Message through a TCP channel.
